[30;1m491 | [0m[35mdef get_final_messages(self) -> List[Message][0m
[30;1m492 | [0m[35m```[0m
[30;1m493 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m494 | [0m[35mThese methods are provided for convenience to collect information at the end of a stream. Calling th[0m
[30;1m495 | [0m[35mwill trigger consumption of the stream until completion and then return the relevant accumulated obj[0m

[30;1m520 | [0m[35m              model considers the results of the tokens with top_p probability mass. So 0.1[0m
[30;1m521 | [0m[35m              means only the tokens comprising the top 10% probability mass are considered.[0m
[30;1m522 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m523 | [0m[35m              We generally recommend altering this or temperature but not both.[0m
[30;1m524 | [0m[35m[0m
